@startuml seq-win
participant Player
participant CLI
participant Game
participant Board

Player -> CLI : "r 3 3"
CLI -> Game : reveal(row=3, col=3)
Game -> Board : reveal(3, 3)
Board --> Game : OK
Game -> Game : check_win()
note right: all safe cells revealed?
Game --> CLI : game_over(win)
CLI --> Player : "You win!"
@enduml
